quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,Ndarahiye kumiyaga isanzazwa bimwe bikwiye
  51,2,Yikorera ibintu biremereye cane
  51,3,Ikagenda nayo n’ubwitonzi ntangere
  51,4,Hanyuma ikayagaba nganya kw’itegeko ry’Imana
  51,5,Mu vy’ukuri muvyo mwemerewe ni vy’ukuri
  51,6,Mu vy’ukuri ntankeka impembo yanyu izoboneka
  51,7,Ndarahiye kuri aya majuru afise amashusho meza
  51,8,Yuko mwebwe mufise imvugo idahuje n’iyindi
  51,9,Ahindurwa n’ukuri kuri iyo mvugo agahindurwa
  51,10,Abadukanyi bw’ibintu bazo honywa
  51,11,Abari mubujuju bajuragizwa n’ubwo bujuju
  51,12,"Babaza bati:- ni ryari umusi w’intahe"
  51,13,Uwo musi bazohanirwa bari mu muriro udahera
  51,14,"Ni muhonje ibihano vyanyu, kuko ibi vyose nivyo mwahora muhimiriza"
  51,15,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tgamburukira\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmu mirima myiza hamwe n’amasoko y’amazi y’umusarara"
  51,16,"Bakira ivyo Umuremyi wabo yabahaye, mu vy’ukuri bahora bagira ineza imbere yibi vyose"
  51,17,Bahora baryama itiro rikeyi cane mugihe c’ijoro
  51,18,Basaba imbabazi mugihe c’imbere y’umutwenzi
  51,19,No mu matungo yabo hari ngombwa yuguha umukene asegereza hamwe n’uwigumya mukuda saba
  51,20,No kuri iy’Isi harimwo ibimenyetso kubafise ivyemezo nyakuri
  51,21,"No mumitima yanyu, mbega ntavyo mubona"
  51,22,No mu Majuru hariho imigisha yanyu kandi mwemerewe
  51,23,Rero ndarahiye ku Muremyi w’Ijuru n’Isi yuko mu vy’ukuri ibi vyose ni vy’ukuri nkuko bimeze n’ingene mubivuga